Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.36,0:00:03.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, what's the Tea \NCeremony Club going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.09,0:00:06.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? As usual, we'll serve tea and\N refreshments in a quiet setting...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:07.73,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Art Museum\NSharpen the Eye of Your Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:07.73,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyaji Academy High School Division\N10 More Days Until the School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:07.73,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Archery
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.28,0:00:08.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You're not gonna do a maid cafe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:12.90,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocks are Beautiful!\NEarth Science Club
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:10.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's low!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:12.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tea Ceremony Club, females, maid cafe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your thinking is way too simplistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:19.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude to girls in tea ceremony \Nclubs all over the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:18.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:19.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.58,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyaji Academy High School \NDivision Student Council
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cardfight Club will participate \Nin the school festival too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:28.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All clubs in this school are required \Nto take part in the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:32.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. We're a brand-new club, so I \Nthought maybe we wouldn't be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:36.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:39.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we open a Cardfight dojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:40.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's also do a card exhibit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:43.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:45.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I forgot to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:52.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't submit an entry beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so right now, the only opening is the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:00:57.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:01:00.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of \Nperformance you'll put on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:05.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Performance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:38.92,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Physics Prep Room\NCardfight Club {\s1}(tentative){\s0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's telling us to put on a play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:43.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since the stage in the gym \Nis the only place we can use...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:46.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows how ridiculous that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:48.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I say we do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Aichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show 'em the strong \Nwill of the Cardfight Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:57.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say this when you're so fired up,\N but preparing a play is no simple thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kourin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:03.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First we'd need a script and staging,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then we'd have to prepare costumes and a set.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do we do that with just five people?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Five people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:14.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, where's Shingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:20.13,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Exciting School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:24.14,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:25.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:26.86,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Marron's Glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:27.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate and Nehalem to the Battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the heck is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.77,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Gancelot Returns!\Nby Shingo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scripts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scripts that I've written \Nover the past several years
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:39.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that are set in the world of Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.90,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Tristan Flies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Can we use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:47.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My debut as a scriptwriter has \Ncome sooner than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi! Leave the costume-making to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:54.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're good at sewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:56.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Emi! Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course! That's my Komoi Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:02.11,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Laughing Invincible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It looks like we \Ncan actually do this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:03.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:08.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everybody, let's all do our \Nbest to make the festival a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:13.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're all excited about it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:18.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What can rank amateur actors \Ndo in just ten days?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll fall on their faces in \Nfront of the whole student body...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The reputation of the Cardfight \NClub will plummet even more,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:27.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,making it only a matter of \Ntime before the club folds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A tea stalk is floating \Nstraight up in my cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like something \Ngood is going to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Misaki is going be in a \Nplay at the school festival?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She has practice, so said she'd \Nbe coming home late for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki's first time on stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki's proud moment! The \Nfirst page of her adolescence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to capture the moment on film!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother's school festival, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, neat! That sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:11.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the reaction \NI expected him to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about Kai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Aichi and the rest are gonna \Nput on a play, then of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kourin is gonna be up on stage, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the reaction \NI expected you to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kourin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:36.56,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bamboo-Cutter\NVanguard
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:39.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long, long ago, there lived \Na Little Sage, Marron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, when Marron went to the \Nmountains to get some bamboo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:47.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,she found the beautiful CEO Amaterasu \Ninside some shining bamboo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:53.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out that King of Knights, Alfred \Nis in love with the beautifully-raised Amaterasu,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but her shy young maiden's \Nheart always stands in her way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so she can never express her true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:02.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tragedy suddenly strikes \Nthis sweet-and-sour couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amaterasu is kidnapped \Nby Vowing Sword Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:10.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The poor thing is shut \Nup inside a dark cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:15.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alfred goes out to save her, \Nfights bravely, and wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Are you okay, Amaterasu?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:21.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I had faith you would come!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I would go anywhere for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:29.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, they live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:30.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:30.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The End!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:35.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this high fantasy \Namalgamation between Vanguard and a fairy tale?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was interesting as heck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:44.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Vowing Sword Dragon \Nwas especially awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to be picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'm going to\N announce the casting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it you get to decide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my script, and I'm going to direct it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:01.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't speak back to the man at the helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:06.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Little Sage, Marron will \Nbe played by Aichi Sendou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vowing Sword Dragon will \Nbe played by Naoki Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Good call!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:16.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The heroine, CEO Amaterasu, \Nwill be Misaki Tokura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the hero, King of Knights, Alfred...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be played by Kourin Tatsunagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:26.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:32.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In my scripts, Kourin of the popular \Ngroup Ultra-rare is the heroic character.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:35.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This will cause a stir and be a colossal \Nsuccess, no two ways about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can even set our sights on Broadway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:44.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki is the perfect \Nchoice to play Amaterasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do my best to make the costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi, you're going to be in it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I play Marron...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go see you and \Nbring my camera along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:57.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, you don't have to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:06.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll capture your performance amazingly, \Nspectacularly and perfectly, Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you don't have to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, our guests who are at the \Npinnacle of popularity, Ultra-rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:19.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Ultra-rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:29.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you can't practice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We suddenly have to tape a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:35.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though every single day 'til \Nthe performance is precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the hero role.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:39.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how actors get once they've \Nexperienced a little success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:50.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start rehearsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:55.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard on her, being an idol as \Nwell as a student here at the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:58.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we've got to \Ndo what we can on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:08:59.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:00.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:04.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And as for Kourin, it'll be fine if \Nshe misses a day or two of practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:08.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendou, please say Kourin's \Nlines in her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:19.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this is where Alfred \Ndefeats Vowing Sword Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:23.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and saves Amaterasu... \Nin a touching scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, Alfred!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:32.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Are you okay, Amaterasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith you would come...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.77,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyaji Academy High School Division\NSchool Festival\N6 Days Left!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:51.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Kourin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! She's as cute as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:58.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doin'?! Walkin' back and forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you freshmen doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! No running in the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of red lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how you learn your lines, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:48.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while working as an idol, this \Nplay is a learning experience for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no big deal! I'm a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:56.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The day before the play, we'll \Nbe doing a run-through from 3:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:59.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can make that with the rest \Nof us, there should be no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I'll be there for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:05.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I had faith you would come..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Amaterasu's line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Page 27, line 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:18.78,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,5 more days until the fest!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:26.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,3 Days Left
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:40.51,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Days remaining until the school festival... 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I left that in the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:54.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The idol seems busy today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:57.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did I forget again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatever! The school \Nisn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:02.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Tatsunagi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had an emergency message to give her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:07.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:10.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:14.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, but would you catch \Nup with her and pass on the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.30,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,School Festival\N{\s1}Days Left{\s0} Tomorrow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kourin ain't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief! She doesn't even bother \Ncoming to the full rehearsal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:36.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she really have any \Ninterest in doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, what's with Kourin standin' us up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really been busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:20.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, today was the full rehearsal! \NYou'd think she'd make it no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my casting choices \Nwere inspired, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:36.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alfred! Sendou should play our hero, Alfred!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:44.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! If Kourin doesn't come \Ntomorrow, Aichi should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta have insurance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, you oughta do it either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'll chuck \NKourin, who's undependable,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:56.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and aim for the star of \NBroadway together with Sendou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's the best way, Aichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:02.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We agree for once, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Not bad, Bowl-cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:07.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Bowl... You had to \Nsneak an insult in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:07.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:08.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:09.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.06,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyaji Academy School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:30.05,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakisoba
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:34.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:40.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you're making him \Nnervous. Don't stare like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're using a good sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a program!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:49.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It says Brother's play starts at 2:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:51.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where're Manager and Lose-umi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.70,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Karate Club Presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:59.50,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kourin Kourin Kourin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.75,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Physics Prep Room\NCardfight Club {\s1}(tentative){\s0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's past noon, already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kourin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Rekka said she'd \Nbe on a shoot today until lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:18.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!\NKourin must be there, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:20.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:23.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she doesn't know how \Nto manage her schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:27.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't deal with these \Nlast-minute schedule changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sendou, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please ride King of Knights, Alfred!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:38.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the play is at 2:00. I'm sure \Nshe'll show up before then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-president?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Were you expecting someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an emergency message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a mistake in the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:54.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry, but the Cardfight Club's\N play will actually start at 1:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:56.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At 1:00?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you just change it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you people study at Miyaji Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:07.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,which churns out the human resources \Nneeded to deal with a global society...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have faith that you'll be able \Nto handle this level of trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,by adapting to the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?! What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things just went from bad to \Nworse! It doubles our trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:29.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a change in the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cardfight Club's performance \Nis going to begin shortly, at 1:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardfight Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the one that formed recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:39.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it could be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! And I hear that girl \Nfrom Ultra-rare is in it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:57.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:00.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! This is Kourin's stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:04.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, help me get Misaki's costume on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:07.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! My hands are full!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:09.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:14.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came after hearing that your \Nperformance was moved up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's just as chaotic as I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Emi Sendou from the \Nmiddle school division.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you guys sure are unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:28.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your full rehearsal was pushed back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and now the actual performance \Nis gonna start early...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about your run-through yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,which was pushed from 3:00 to 5:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The vice-president...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:47.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He had me tell Kourin that \Nthe time was changed to 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.72,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardfight Club\NLove and Youthful Vanguard
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki... Kourin will come, won't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:08.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:21.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long, long ago, there lived \Na Little Sage, Marron.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?! What's that glowing bamboo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Marron splits the glowing bamboo,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:34.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the beautiful CEO Amaterasu, \Nof all things, is born!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:41.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amaterasu is raised beautifully...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, tragedy strikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:51.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Vowing Sword Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking Amaterasu with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:59.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amaterasu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:05.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amaterasu is shut inside \Nthe Celestial Rock Cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the hero that appears to save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:12.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...actually appear to save her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:17.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Suck it up, Aichi. Come on, \Nput this on and fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:23.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The story can't finish 'til \NAlfred appears and beats me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:27.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! It doesn't look like Kourin's \Ngonna be here, so forget about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:31.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. We have to \Nhandle this somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:35.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for Kourin's sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There ya go! That's the Aichi I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be waitin' for you on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't part of the show, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:01.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your act together, Cardfight Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:06.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about this?! Where's Kourin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Get Ultra-rare out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:10.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we came here to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:15.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't get to see Kourin, \Nthere was no point in coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see Kourin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. The budget they were \Ngiven was too small after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:26.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for a \Ncheaply-built set to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:39.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is... Is this my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:44.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over... My script...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:47.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My stage... My Broadway...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Aichi... I'm sorry, \NBoss Lady... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:54.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not your fault, Naoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This, that, everything \Nis the fault of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:00.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Amaterasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:18.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One second later and I would've blamed it \Nall on this impossible script of Shingo Komoi's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... By "this," you meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patience!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:27.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero, King of Knights, Alfred, is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you, Kourin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith you would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness she got here in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but this is wrecked...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:46.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've reached the climax at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:49.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alfred's battle is going to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:53.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon you're supposed to \Nfight can't come out any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:55.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:58.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The true enemy that I'm going to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:01.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:08.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Daigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:12.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-D-D-D-Daigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:16.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The genuine legendary \Nfighter, Daigo, is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:18.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:58.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the legendary fighter, Daigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:01.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daigo?! He's cool, sure, but is he strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:02.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.67,0:24:05.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to Vanguard, he's God-plus!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:09.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I never imagined I'd get \Nto see Daigo fight at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:11.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Legendary School Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.42,0:24:24.90,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary School Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:13.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What will the outcome of the fight be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.46,0:24:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what about the play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:16.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! I expected something like \Nthis would happen, so I plotted it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:22.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This was all part of my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.64,0:24:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You total liar!!